- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper applies concepts from causal reasoning, itemset mining, and logic programming to analyze the data.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper may have used machine learning techniques for itemset mining and modeling new semantic structures.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is possible as the paper may have developed new algorithms or extended existing ones.
- cs.DB (Databases) is possible as the paper deals with analyzing data collected from over 400 D2web hacker forums.
